title: No. 21 Virginia Tech primed for Tuesday tilt at Liberty - VT hokiesports.com
content: No. 21 Virginia Tech primed for Tuesday tilt at Liberty  VT hokiesports.com
description: Vaulting into D1Baseball's top 25 rankings for the first time this season, the Virginia Tech baseball team (20-8) will look to keep its foot on the gas pedal on Tuesday, April 12, when Tech treks to Lynchburg for a midweek matchup against Liberty (20-10) at the Liberty Baseball Stadium.
